An [[exchange|currency_exchange]] site serving those buying bitcoins with U.S. dollars (USD), Australian dollars (AUD) and Indian rupees (INR).

The price at which the bitcoins are bought is specifed at the time the order is placed.

##Buying Bitcoins

###USD

* Cash deposit (Major banks, 7-11, Walmart, CVS, etc.)

###AUD

* Cash deposit (Westpack or Commonwealth Bank)

###RUB

* Cash deposit (Qiwi or Cyberplat)

###BRL

* Cash deposit (Boleto or Banco Recomendito)

###INR

* Cash deposit (HDFC Bank throughout India)

##History

The service was launched May 28, 2012 (8.1).  The company operated by the same company that operates [[CryptoXChange]].

